n: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.arsenal.com/sites/default/files/wallpaper/facup2017_2_1920x1080_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.arsenal.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fwallpaper%2Ffacup2017_2_1920x1080_0.jpg&h=41c70e98&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://paininthearsenal.com/wp-content/uploads/getty-images/2017/08/826971802-chelsea-v-arsenal-the-fa-community-shield.jpg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaininthearsenal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fgetty-images%2F2017%2F08%2F826971802-chelsea-v-arsenal-the-fa-community-shield.jpg.jpg&h=c4697e47&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"a1bed75c9fad6ae8914810223426aa4c4f8d20a3","tid":931917,"uid":61902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:07:07.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"491611b59dac30183ee34f1c98f11b9e32e278aa","tid":931917,"uid":34217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:07:48.000Z","msg":"推呢個"},{"pid":"c23d34987a2f49540a462cc85ee040a3fe4e03fc","tid":931917,"uid":8404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c22597da229ff67efbd70aa9f27e43fc2f4008","tid":931917,"uid":15842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:08:43.000Z","msg":"樓下係狗"},{"pid":"fdb4d1c3e2f364d5ff70175ab9047b16c83a4520","tid":931917,"uid":10089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:09:05.000Z","msg":"反彈"},{"pid":"478b46aaa13468b6d09ed84a63a97a98fcf1c694","tid":931917,"uid":53121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:16:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鑽石眼：關於簽約古恩杜斯</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n槍手今夏從洛里昂以不到800萬磅的價格簽下了年輕人古恩杜斯，但槍手招募主管解釋了他們如何長期觀察這名中場的--那要追溯到上上個賽季當他們還在法甲，當時接近17歲的小伙在法甲得到了8次出場機會。<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgsa.baidu.com/forum/w%3D580/sign=311f818a25381f309e198da199004c67/15e3562c11dfa9ec2523e5a56fd0f703918fc120.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgsa.baidu.com%2Fforum%2Fw%253D580%2Fsign%3D311f818a25381f309e198da199004c67%2F15e3562c11dfa9ec2523e5a56fd0f703918fc120.jpg&h=1b9f56d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">鑽石眼透露，當他考察古恩杜斯時，他關注了球員的弱點而不是強項，試圖判斷那些方面能不能通過訓練得到足夠的提高。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我是在洛里昂注意到他的，當時他們還在法甲，&rdquo;鑽石眼說道。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我喜歡那家球隊，他們總能培養出有趣的球員。古恩杜斯因他的長頭髮和個性而很顯眼。&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;但我也特別關注了他的弱點。那些可以訓練嗎？他總會不必要的滿場飛奔，但我很確定這僅僅是訓練和時間的問題，然後他會學會跑動的時機。&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;這是一筆重要的交易，因為我們想要讓世界看到--我們還是那支阿仙奴，那支給年輕人機會的俱樂部。&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n在多蒙特曾經發現多名才俊的鑽石眼解釋了他在多蒙特和在阿仙奴的角色，那不僅僅是發現球員，而且他也參與招募流程的方方面面。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我是做出下一任主帥也就是艾美利任命的選擇團隊成員之一，&rdquo;他解釋道。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;而'招募主管'意味著我不僅僅是找到目標，而且也要讓他們簽下合同。&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;甚至當我在多蒙特時也沒有明顯的職責區分。像我們從巴黎簽下的Dan-Axel Aagadou ，以及從曼城簽下的Sancho，我都跟經紀人、球員和他們的父母們談判。&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n對於在英格蘭他面臨的挑戰，他認為競爭對手的強大是槍手必需面對的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;如果消息洩露出去說我們想要簽下誰，（馬上）至少兩支不同的球隊會加入抬價，&rdquo;他說。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;在英超有至少三支'拜仁'：曼徹斯特兩家以及車路士。而另外還有三家'多蒙特'：利物浦、熱刺和阿仙奴。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;這是個不一樣的競爭。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"2f70522af367959921264e46d96ae057d48561de","tid":931917,"uid":11055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:17:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開左又開"},{"pid":"4b66cbbef4797823d51f0bde47bbfd64bb2f2fc1","tid":931917,"uid":53121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2f70522af367959921264e46d96ae057d48561de","tid":931917,"uid":11055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:17:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset